<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Job Recommendation</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: white;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Navbar styles */
        .navbar {
            background-color: #AF8F6F;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-right: auto; /* Push the brand to the left */
        }

        .navbar-nav {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar-nav li {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .navbar-nav li:first-child {
            margin-left: 0;
        }

        .navbar-nav li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 + p {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #302f2f;
    
        }


        h1 {
            text-align: center; 
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            color: #ad7b54;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-family: fantas;
            font-style: italic;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
    
        }
        h2{
            text-align: center; 
            font-size: 2rem;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            color: #ad7b54;
            
        }

        
            .card {
        background-color: #fff;
        background-image: url("i4.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 10px; /* Increase padding */
        margin: 70px auto; /* Center the card horizontally */
        max-width: 1000px; /* Adjusted width */
        height: 400px; /* Adjusted height */
        position: relative; /* Relative positioning for the container */
     }


        .card-input {
            position: absolute; /* Absolute positioning for the card */
            top: 50%; /* Center the card vertically */
            left: 50%; /* Center the card horizontally */
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background-color: rgba(235, 232, 232, 0.635); /* Transparent background for the card */
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(91, 91, 91, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 400px; /* Limit the width of the card */
            max-height: 200px;
            width: calc(100% - 80px); /* Adjusted width */
            height: calc(100% - 80px); /* Adjusted height */
        }

        label {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        button[type="submit"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #AF8F6F;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        button[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #AF8F6F;
        }


        .image-container img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        
        .description {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .recommendation-cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .recommendation-card {
            width: calc(50% - 20px); /* Adjusted width for two cards per row */
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            min-height: 200px; /* Set a minimum height */
            display: flex; /* Use flexbox to allow dynamic height */
            flex-direction: column; /* Align content in a column */
        }

        .recommendation-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .recommendation-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #AF8F6f;
        }

        .recommendation-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
            flex-grow: 1; /* Allow the paragraph to grow dynamically */
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-brand">CAREER CATALYST</div>
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i> Trending News</a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="#"><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Reviews</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Don't be pushed around by the fears in your mind.<br>Be led by the dreams in your heart.</h1>
        <p>Explore Your Interests: Begin your career journey by exploring your interests, hobbies, and passions.<br>Consider what activities bring you joy and fulfillment.Your interests can provide valuable insights into potential career paths.</p>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-input">
                    <form id="job-finder" action="/career" method="post" >
                        <div class="input-container">
                            <label for="qualifications">Education</label>
                            <input type="text" id="c_education" name="c_education" required><br>
                            <label for="skills">Interests</label>
                            <input type="text" id="Details" name="Details" required><br>
                            <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
    
        <h2>Your Exclusive Suggestions</h2>
        <div class="recommendation-cards">
            <% if (locals.result) { %>
           
                <div class="recommendation-card">
                    <textarea rows="50" cols="50">
                    <h3>career</h3>
                    <p>Description of recommended job...</p>
                    <p>- career range: <%= result %></p>
                </div>
                        <h2> no related job found </h2>
                        <% } %>
                    </textarea>

                </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    

    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.3/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
